<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.3.3">
<l>ētu ceytāl maṟakkēṉ maṉamē toḻutumeḻu</l>
<l>tātu malku taṭañcūḻ poḻiltāḻ vartoṭarntupiṉ</l>
<l>pētai niṉṉaip piriyē ṉiṉiyeṉ ṟakaṉṟāṉiṭam</l>
<l>pōtu nāḷuṅ kamaḻum poḻilcūḻn tapullāṇiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I will forget [him] if I do what? Arise, [my] heart; we will worship</l>
<l>In Pullāṇi, encircled by groves scented by the day’s [new] buds,</l>
<l>The place of the one who, having followed me into an arbor in a grove</l>
<l rend="indent">surrounded by pollen-filled ponds,</l>
<l>[And] having said, “Foolish [girl], I will not desert you from now on,” then left.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
